# Payment Settings — Charges Section

Settings → Payment Settings uses a Table/Listing (with vertical separators, `grid-cols-[1fr_1.5fr_0.5fr]`) for payment instruments, charges, and status across QR, Card Machine, and Payment Links tabs.

## Charges Column Rules
- All charges text: `font-weight: 400` (normal) — NEVER `font-semibold`
- Tiered pricing: `flex flex-col gap-1`
- Tier label: `text-[#7e7e7e]` (muted)
- Tier value: `text-[#101010]` (foreground)
- Single value: `text-[14px] text-[#101010]`
- Free: `text-[#21c179]` (success green, no bold)
- Indented sub-tiers: `ml-4`

## Hyperlinks in Charges
- "View Special Cards" / "Know More": `text-[#004299] text-[12px] font-semibold hover:underline`
- This `font-semibold` on the `<a>` is the ONLY bold allowed in the charges column

## Pattern
```tsx
<div className="flex flex-col gap-1">
  <p className="text-[14px] leading-[24px]">
    <span className="text-[#7e7e7e]">Up to ₹20,000 / month : </span>
    <span className="text-[#101010]">3% + GST</span>
  </p>
  <a href="#" className="text-[#004299] text-[12px] font-semibold hover:underline mt-1">
    View Special Cards
  </a>
</div>
```
